data.description: Discover the perfect blend of nature and potential with this 20 acre property. Nestled in the picturesque location you will find this home which is currently undergoing renovations to be transformed into a 4 bedroom and 3 bath spacious oasis. With a large majority of the renovation complete and most materials on site to finish, your dream home is just a finishing touch away. This landscape offers privacy from any neighbors and excellent hunting opportunities. Surrounded by beautiful trees, your yard becomes your own tranquil setting and the perfect escape from the hustle and bustle of town. Round pen, loafing shed, small traps and fenced for livestock. Storage shed in backyard, playhouse of the children, dog pen, carport, and storm cellar for ensured safety during inclement weather. Gated entry. This property is a rare combination of outdoor adventures and your families dream home. Located 3 miles off scenic HWY 412. Less than 15 minutes to Locust Grove.
